description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for salaried GP to join our friendly team at our semi-rural practice with its idyllic location overlooking the beautiful Rother valley. We have a full complement of GPs and nursing staff, as well as a strong supportive administrative team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be available for four to six sessions per week, and will be passionate about delivering high quality healthcare.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We aim to provide sustainable quality care to our community. With that vision we provide a high GP session to patient ratio and offer 10 or 20 minute appointments based on patient need.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer a taste of traditional general practice with a future focused team, if this sounds tempting please get in touch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information, an informal visit or to apply for this role contact Julie Watson on 01435 882306 or&lt;strong&gt;julie.watson17@nhs.net&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
